{"tid":1399479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城online防守技能篇] - BB彈之運用","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:41:10.000Z","uid":13866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7e13405ca66633bec64bcb8558522226da9ddf","tid":1399479,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"［香城online防守技能篇] -BB彈之運用<br />\n道具: BB彈+偈油<br />\n<br />\n  依幾日香城online又更新，除左普通低級狗隻，仲有好多快速惡狗出沒。下列戰法供大家掩護撤退之用。<br />\n  狗隻弱點: 狗Boot不防滑。所以針對沙田副本一役，點樣令狗仔訓低係關鍵。依個時候就要用到BB彈 (6-7mm最佳!)。<br />\n技能發動:<br />\n<br />\n1）當人類同狗隻互相設立防線時，bb彈開始分發俾人類前缐。每條行車線需要一包1000發BB彈!<br />\n2)  佈防時係人類和狗隻之間空位撒BB彈。唔好剩係等狗仔衝過嚟啊! <br />\n(PS:記得盡量係中間同平路撒啊!)<br />\n3) 當快速惡狗推進時，前線一路走佬，一路倒BB彈。想要加成效果，仲可以加埋枝偈油用 [深水埗孖八買偈油平！]!<br />\n<br />\n下回再教大家點掩護撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe89c00aa83bdf51142a1187af04f795f4f58448","tid":1399479,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"8月5 全民三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3d6c26ba31d9bb22c31c9aa9e2dfd0beff791f","tid":1399479,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"8月5 全民三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6964cbb538ad9acd7c68b604a3c456ae2ae4066f","tid":1399479,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"8月5 全民三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a2a34292ccff950bf459f615a0efc2c498443c","tid":1399479,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"bb彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電池<